<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c2">(وَ)</span> السَّابِعُ: <span class="c2">(طَوَافُ وَدَاعٍ)</span>.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c2">(وَأَرْكَانُ العُمْرَةِ: ثَلَاثَةٌ)</span>:<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">الأَوَّلُ:</span> <span class="c2">(إِحْرَامٌ)</span>.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c2">(وَ)</span> الثَّانِي: <span class="c2">(طَوَافٌ)</span>.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c2">(وَ)</span> الثَّالِثُ: <span class="c2">(سَعْيٌ)</span>.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c2">(وَوَاجِبُهَا: اِثْنَانِ)</span>:<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c5">الأَوَّلُ:</span> <span class="c2">(الإِحْرَامُ مِنَ الحِلِّ)</span>.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c2">(وَ)</span> الثَّانِي: <span class="c2">(الْحَلْقُ أَوِ التَّقْصِيرُ)</span>.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c2">(وَمَنْ فَاتَهُ الوُقُوفُ: فَاتَهُ الحَجُّ)</span>، وَسَقَطَ عَنْهُ تَوَابِعُ الوُقُوفِ، <span class="c2">(وَتَحَلَّلَ بِعُمْرَةٍ وَهَدْيٍ إِنْ لَمْ يَكُنِ اِشْتَرطَ)</span> فِي ابْتِدَاءِ إِحْرَامِهِ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c2">(وَمَنْ)</span> أَحْرَمَ ثُمَّ <span class="c2">(مُنِعَ البَيْتَ: أَهْدَى، ثُمَّ حَلَّ، فَإِنْ فَقَدَهُ)</span> أَيِ الهَدْيَ أَوْ ثَمَنَهُ: <span class="c2">(صَامَ عَشَرَةَ أَيَّامٍ)</span>.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c2">(وَمَنْ صُدَّ عَنْ عَرَفَةَ: تَحَلَّلَ)</span> قَبْلَ فَوَاتِ الحَجِّ <span class="c2">(بِعُمْرَةٍ)</span>، وَلَا قَضَاءَ عَلَيْهِ، <span class="c2">(وَلَا دَمَ)</span>.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c2">(فَصْلٌ)</span> فِي الهَدْيِ وَالأُضْحِيَّةِ وَالعَقِيقَةِ<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c2">(وَالْأُضْحِيَّةُ سُنَّةٌ)</span> مُؤَكَّدَةٌ لِمُسْلِمٍ، <span class="c2">(يُكْرَهُ تَرْكُهَا لِقَادِرٍ)</span> عَلَيْهَا.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span><span class="c2">(وَوَقْتُ الذَّبْحِ: بَعْدَ صَلَاةِ العِيدِ، أَوْ)</span> بَعْدَ <span class="c2">(قَدْرِهَا)</span> أَيِ الصَّلَاةِ <span class="c2">(إِلَى آخِرِ ثَانِي)</span> أَيَّامِ <span class="c2">(التَّشْرِيقِ)</span>.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span><span class="c2">(وَلَا يُعْطَى جَازِرٌ أُجَرْتَهُ مِنْهَا)</span>، وَلَهُ إِعْطَاؤُهُ هَدِيَّةً وَصَدَقَةً، <span class="c2">(وَلَا يُبَاعُ جِلْدُهَا، وَلَا شَيْءٌ مِنْهَا؛ بَلْ)</span> يَتَصَدَّقُ أَوْ <span class="c2">(يَنْتَفِعُ بِهِ)</span>.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>